      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"alz-section alz-encmp alz-reveal is-visible\" style=\"padding: 60px 0; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #141b4d 0%, #44448d 100%); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;\">\n  <div class=\"alz-container\" style=\"max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px;\">\n\n    <header class=\"alz-encmp__head\" style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 40px;\">\n      <p class=\"alz-eyebrow\" style=\"text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 12px; color: #fea403; font-weight: 600;\">Consommation</p>\n      <h2 class=\"alz-encmp__title\" style=\"font-size: 2.8rem; margin: 0 0 20px 0; font-weight: 500; color: #fff; letter-spacing: -1px;\">\n        18 W. Une ampoule LED.\n      </h2>\n      <p class=\"alz-lede\" style=\"font-size: 1.25rem; color: #c7c9e6; max-width: 650px; margin: 0 auto; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: normal;\">\n        Sur une saison de 4 mois, ce ventilateur consomme moins de 9€ d'électricité. Une climatisation équivalente : ~960€.\n      </p>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"alz-encmp__grid\" style=\"display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 24px; max-width: 850px; margin: 0 auto 32px auto;\">\n\n      <div class=\"alz-encmp__card alz-encmp__card--alize\" style=\"flex: 1; min-width: 250px; background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15); border-radius: 24px; padding: 32px 24px; text-align: center; backdrop-filter: blur(6px);\">\n        <p class=\"alz-encmp__card-label\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: #fea403; letter-spacing: 1px; margin: 0 0 16px 0;\">ALIZÉ</p>\n        <div class=\"alz-encmp__watts\" style=\"margin-bottom: 12px;\">\n          <span class=\"alz-encmp__watts-num\" style=\"font-size: 4rem; font-weight: 700; color: #fff; line-height: 1; letter-spacing: normal;\">18</span>\n          <span class=\"alz-encmp__watts-unit\" style=\"font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; color: #fff; vertical-align: super; margin-left: 2px; letter-spacing: normal;\">W</span>\n        </div>\n        <p class=\"alz-encmp__card-eq\" style=\"font-size: 15px; color: #c7c9e6; margin: 0 0 24px 0; letter-spacing: normal;\">Comme une ampoule LED</p>\n        <div class=\"alz-encmp__cost\" style=\"border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15); padding-top: 16px;\">\n          <p class=\"alz-encmp__cost-label\" style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #9b9dca; text-transform: uppercase; margin: 0 0 4px 0; letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">Coût annuel estimé*</p>\n          <p class=\"alz-encmp__cost-value\" style=\"font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; color: #fff; margin: 0; letter-spacing: normal;\">≈ 5 €</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"alz-encmp__ratio\" style=\"text-align: center; flex-shrink: 0; padding: 0 10px;\">\n        <div class=\"alz-encmp__ratio-num\" style=\"font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 700; color: #fea403; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 1.1;\">×111</div>\n        <p class=\"alz-encmp__ratio-text\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #fea403; font-weight: 600; margin: 4px 0 0 0; letter-spacing: normal;\">moins gourmand</p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"alz-encmp__card alz-encmp__card--clim\" style=\"flex: 1; min-width: 250px; background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 24px; padding: 32px 24px; text-align: center; backdrop-filter: blur(6px);\">\n        <p class=\"alz-encmp__card-label\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: #c7c9e6; letter-spacing: 1px; margin: 0 0 16px 0;\">Climatisation</p>\n        <div class=\"alz-encmp__watts\" style=\"margin-bottom: 12px;\">\n          <span class=\"alz-encmp__watts-num\" style=\"font-size: 4rem; font-weight: 500; color: #c7c9e6; line-height: 1; letter-spacing: normal;\">2000</span>\n          <span class=\"alz-encmp__watts-unit\" style=\"font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 500; color: #c7c9e6; vertical-align: super; margin-left: 2px; letter-spacing: normal;\">W</span>\n        </div>\n        <p class=\"alz-encmp__card-eq\" style=\"font-size: 15px; color: #9b9dca; margin: 0 0 24px 0; letter-spacing: normal;\">Comme un four électrique</p>\n        <div class=\"alz-encmp__cost\" style=\"border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding-top: 16px;\">\n          <p class=\"alz-encmp__cost-label\" style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #9b9dca; text-transform: uppercase; margin: 0 0 4px 0; letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">Coût annuel estimé*</p>\n          <p class=\"alz-encmp__cost-value\" style=\"font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; color: #c7c9e6; margin: 0; letter-spacing: normal;\">≈ 576 €</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"alz-encmp__savings\" role=\"note\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 12px; background-color: rgba(254,164,3,0.15); border: 1px solid rgba(254,164,3,0.3); border-radius: 16px; padding: 16px 24px; max-width: 850px; margin: 0 auto 32px auto; box-sizing: border-box; color: #fff;\">\n      <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#fea403\" stroke-width=\"1.6\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"flex-shrink: 0;\">\n        <path d=\"M12 2v20M5 7c0-2 2-3 7-3s7 1 7 3-2 3-7 3-7 1-7 3 2 3 7 3 7 1 7 3-2 3-7 3-7-1-7-3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path>\n      </svg>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: normal;\">\n        <strong style=\"font-weight: 700; color: #fea403;\">Vous économisez environ 571 € par saison</strong> en remplaçant la clim par un ventilateur ALIZÉ.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <p class=\"alz-encmp__footnote\" style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 13px; color: #9b9dca; margin-top: 35px; font-style: italic; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: normal; max-width: 750px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n      *Estimation basée sur 8h/jour, 4 mois/an, prix kWh 0.3 € (tarif réglementé EDF). L'écart réel dépend de votre usage et de votre fournisseur d'électricité.\n    </p>\n\n  </div>\n</div>",
        "padding_top": 0,
        "padding_bottom": 0
      }
