    "custom_liquid_gqprFw": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "name": "t:sections.custom-liquid.presets.name",
      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<section id=\"shopify-section-template--28557026754942__store_faq_QKxkLH\" class=\"shopify-section section\">\n\n<!-- Apply mobile fonts immediately on page load -->\n<script>\n  (function () {\n    if (window.innerWidth < 750) {\n      document.documentElement.classList.add('faq-mobile-view');\n    }\n  })();\n</script>\n\n<div class=\"store-faq-section \" style=\"\n    \n    padding-top: 30px;\n    padding-bottom: 30px;\n    \n\n    \n      \n      background-color: #ffffff !important;\n    \n\n    \n\n    \n  \">\n  <div class=\"store-faq-container\" style=\"\n      width: 100%;\n      max-width: 1200px;\n      margin: 0 auto;\n    \">\n    \n      \n\n\n<div class=\"page-width store-faq-flex-container center-no-image\">\n  <div class=\"store-faq-header-column\">\n    \n      <h2 class=\"store-faq-heading\" style=\"color: #1b2025 !important; font-size: 26px;\">\n        FAQ\n      </h2>\n    \n\n    \n\n    <div class=\"store-faq\" id=\"store-faq-template--28557026754942__store_faq_QKxkLH\" style=\"\n        width: 100%;\n        margin: 0 auto;\n      \">\n        <!-- Single Column Layout (Default) -->\n        <div class=\"store-faq-items-container border-bottom-only individual-borders\" style=\"border-radius: 8px;\" data-accordion=\"true\">\n          \n            \n                <div class=\"store-faq-item\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e5e5 !important;\">\n                  <div class=\"store-faq-question\" style=\"\n                      color: #1b2025 !important;\n                      background-color: #e0eefd !important;\n                      --question-padding-top: 25px;\n                      --question-padding-bottom: 15px;\n                      --question-padding-left: 20px;\n                      --question-padding-right: 20px;\n                    \">\n                    <span>Comment on l'installe ?</span>\n                    <span class=\"store-faq-toggle\">+</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"store-faq-answer\" style=\"\n                      color: #1b2025 !important;\n                      background-color: #ffffff !important;\n                      --answer-padding-top: 15px;\n                      --answer-padding-bottom: 15px;\n                      --answer-padding-left: 20px;\n                      --answer-padding-right: 20px;\n                    \">\n                    <p>Vous coupez le courant, vous retirez votre ampoule et vous vissez le ventilateur sur la douille E27. Pour une stabilité maximale, vous fixez le support fourni au plafond. Comptez moins de 10 minutes, sans électricien ni câblage.</p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n            \n          \n            \n                <div class=\"store-faq-item\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e5e5 !important;\">\n                  <div class=\"store-faq-question\" style=\"\n                      color: #1b2025 !important;\n                      background-color: #e0eefd !important;\n                      --question-padding-top: 25px;\n                      --question-padding-bottom: 15px;\n                      --question-padding-left: 20px;\n                      --question-padding-right: 20px;\n                    \">\n                    <span>C'est compatible avec ma douille ? Je suis locataire.</span>\n                    <span class=\"store-faq-toggle\">+</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"store-faq-answer\" style=\"\n                      color: #1b2025 !important;\n                      background-color: #ffffff !important;\n                      --answer-padding-top: 15px;\n                      --answer-padding-bottom: 15px;\n                      --answer-padding-left: 20px;\n                      --answer-padding-right: 20px;\n                    \">\n                    <p>Oui, sur les douilles E27 standard, à condition qu'elle soit bien fixée au plafond. Aucune intervention sur l'électricité n'est nécessaire, c'est donc adapté à la location. Le support à vis fourni sert uniquement à renforcer la stabilité.</p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n            \n          \n            \n                <div class=\"store-faq-item\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e5e5 !important;\">\n                  <div class=\"store-faq-question\" style=\"\n                      color: #1b2025 !important;\n                      background-color: #e0eefd !important;\n                      --question-padding-top: 25px;\n                      --question-padding-bottom: 15px;\n                      --question-padding-left: 20px;\n                      --question-padding-right: 20px;\n                    \">\n                    <span>Est-ce assez puissant pour ma pièce ?</span>\n                    <span class=\"store-faq-toggle\">+</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"store-faq-answer\" style=\"\n                      color: #1b2025 !important;\n                      background-color: #ffffff !important;\n                      --answer-padding-top: 15px;\n                      --answer-padding-bottom: 15px;\n                      --answer-padding-left: 20px;\n                      --answer-padding-right: 20px;\n                    \">\n                    <p>Il est conçu pour les chambres, bureaux, studios et petites pièces jusqu'à environ 15 m². Le flux d'air se ressent au centre de la pièce. Pour un grand salon ouvert, mieux vaut un ventilateur plus large.</p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n            \n          \n            \n                <div class=\"store-faq-item\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e5e5 !important;\">\n                  <div class=\"store-faq-question\" style=\"\n                      color: #1b2025 !important;\n                      background-color: #e0eefd !important;\n                      --question-padding-top: 25px;\n                      --question-padding-bottom: 15px;\n                      --question-padding-left: 20px;\n                      --question-padding-right: 20px;\n                    \">\n                    <span>Est-ce que c'est silencieux pour dormir ?</span>\n                    <span class=\"store-faq-toggle\">+</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"store-faq-answer\" style=\"\n                      color: #1b2025 !important;\n                      background-color: #ffffff !important;\n                      --answer-padding-top: 15px;\n                      --answer-padding-bottom: 15px;\n                      --answer-padding-left: 20px;\n                      --answer-padding-right: 20px;\n                    \">\n                    <p>En petite vitesse, il est conçu pour rester discret et convient à un usage nocturne dans une petite pièce. Les vitesses plus élevées se font davantage entendre, comme tout ventilateur. Ce n'est pas un appareil totalement silencieux, mais un brassage doux la nuit.</p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n            \n          \n            \n                <div class=\"store-faq-item\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e5e5 !important;\">\n                  <div class=\"store-faq-question\" style=\"\n                      color: #1b2025 !important;\n                      background-color: #e0eefd !important;\n                      --question-padding-top: 25px;\n                      --question-padding-bottom: 15px;\n                      --question-padding-left: 20px;\n                      --question-padding-right: 20px;\n                    \">\n                    <span>Est-ce que ça tient bien, et est-ce sûr ?</span>\n                    <span class=\"store-faq-toggle\">+</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"store-faq-answer\" style=\"\n                      color: #1b2025 !important;\n                      background-color: #ffffff !important;\n                      --answer-padding-top: 15px;\n                      --answer-padding-bottom: 15px;\n                      --answer-padding-left: 20px;\n                      --answer-padding-right: 20px;\n                    \">\n                    <p>Le ventilateur se visse dans la douille et le support à vis fourni renforce la fixation au plafond. Une fois posé, les pales restent en hauteur, hors de portée des enfants et des animaux. Suivez la notice pour un montage stable.</p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n            \n          \n            \n                <div class=\"store-faq-item\" style=\"\">\n                  <div class=\"store-faq-question\" style=\"\n                      color: #1b2025 !important;\n                      background-color: #e0eefd !important;\n                      --question-padding-top: 25px;\n                      --question-padding-bottom: 15px;\n                      --question-padding-left: 20px;\n                      --question-padding-right: 20px;\n                    \">\n                    <span>Et si la télécommande tombe en panne ?</span>\n                    <span class=\"store-faq-toggle\">+</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"store-faq-answer\" style=\"\n                      color: #1b2025 !important;\n                      background-color: #ffffff !important;\n                      --answer-padding-top: 15px;\n                      --answer-padding-bottom: 15px;\n                      --answer-padding-left: 20px;\n                      --answer-padding-right: 20px;\n                    \">\n                    <p>La télécommande est incluse et pilote la lumière, la vitesse et la minuterie. En cas de problème, vous êtes couvert par la garantie 30 jours et notre support français, avec remplacement selon conditions.</p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n            \n          \n        </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"store-faq-content-column\">\n    \n    \n      \n    \n  </div>\n</div>\n    \n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<style>\n  .store-faq-section {\n    \n    padding: 30px 0;\n    \n    overflow-x: hidden; /* Prevent horizontal overflow at section level */\n  }\n\n  \n  \n\n  \n  @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {\n    .store-faq-section {\n      \n    }\n  }\n\n  .store-faq-container {\n    width: 100%;\n    max-width: 1200px; /* Set max-width here instead of inline */\n    margin: 0 auto;\n    padding-left: 15px;\n    padding-right: 15px;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n  }\n\n  .store-faq-items-container.border-bottom-only {\n    border: none !important;\n  }\n  .store-faq-items-container.border-bottom-only .store-faq-question {\n    padding-right: var(--question-padding-right, 20px) !important;\n    padding-left: var(--question-padding-left, 20px) !important;\n  }\n  .store-faq-items-container.border-bottom-only .store-faq-answer {\n    padding-right: var(--answer-padding-right, 20px) !important;\n    padding-left: var(--answer-padding-left, 20px) !important;\n  }\n\n  .store-faq-flex-container {\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    width: 100%;\n    max-width: 100%;\n  }\n\n  .store-faq-header-column {\n    margin-bottom: 30px;\n    width: 100%;\n    max-width: 100%;\n  }\n\n  .store-faq-content-column {\n    width: 100%;\n    max-width: 100%;\n  }\n\n  .store-faq-heading {\n    margin-bottom: 15px;\n    letter-spacing: var(--letter-spacing-heading);\n    font-size: 26px;\n    line-height: 1.2;\n    word-wrap: break-word;\n    overflow-wrap: break-word;\n  }\n\n  .store-faq-subtitle {\n    line-height: 1.5;\n    max-width: 100%;\n    font-weight: var(--font-weight-regular);\n    letter-spacing: var(--letter-spacing-body);\n    word-wrap: break-word;\n    overflow-wrap: break-word;\n    margin-bottom: 24px;\n  }\n\n  .store-faq-header-image {\n    margin-top: 20px;\n  }\n\n  .store-faq-header-image img {\n    width: 100%;\n    height: auto;\n    display: block;\n  }\n\n  /* Full height image styling - base styles */\n  .store-faq-header-image.full-height {\n    margin: 0;\n    height: 100%;\n    overflow: hidden;\n  }\n\n  .store-faq-header-image.full-height img {\n    width: 100%;\n    height: 100%;\n    object-fit: cover;\n    object-position: center;\n  }\n\n  /* Hide image on mobile */\n  .desktop-only {\n    display: none;\n  }\n\n  .store-faq {\n    width: 100%;\n    max-width: 100%;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n  }\n\n  #store-faq-template--28557026754942__store_faq_QKxkLH .store-faq-items-container {\n    overflow: hidden !important;\n    width: 100% !important;\n    max-width: 100% !important;\n    box-sizing: border-box !important;\n    \n      border: none !important;\n    \n    border-radius: 8px !important;\n  }\n\n  .store-faq .store-faq-item {\n    width: 100%;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n  }\n\n  /* Single column layout - remove bottom border from last item only when container has border */\n  .store-faq .store-faq-items-container:not(.individual-borders) .store-faq-item:last-child {\n    border-bottom: none !important;\n    margin-bottom: 0 !important;\n  }\n\n  /* Two column layout - keep bottom border on last items in columns for visual consistency */\n  .store-faq-flex-container.two-column-desktop .store-faq-items-container:not(.individual-borders) .store-faq-item:last-child {\n    border-bottom: none !important;\n    margin-bottom: 0 !important;\n  }\n\n  /* Container border handles the bottom border, avoid double border */\n  \n\n  /* Border-bottom-only style - ensure last item has border */\n  \n  .store-faq-items-container.border-bottom-only .store-faq-item:last-child {\n    border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e5e5 !important;\n  }\n  \n\n  .store-faq .store-faq-question {\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: space-between;\n    align-items: center;\n    padding: var(--question-padding-top, 15px) var(--question-padding-right, 20px) var(--question-padding-bottom, 15px) var(--question-padding-left, 20px);\n    cursor: pointer;\n    font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);\n